      <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
         <head>Biographical History</head>
         
      <p>Jen Cruse is a collector, scholar, and writer on antique combs.  She is the author of <emph render="italic">The Comb: Its History and Development</emph> (Robert Hale, 2007), and has a personal collection of well over 1,500 combs spanning nearly 2000 years.</p></bioghist>
      
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
         <p>The <emph render="bold">Jen Cruse Antique Comb Collection</emph> consists of 25 antique combs, with the collector's research notes.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      
